#1 Ileocecal valve malignancy
Discussed laparoscopic and open right hemicolectomy.  She would like to proceed as soon as possible.  She will need a CT-scan abdomen and pelvis to rule-out liver metastases ahead of surgery.  We will try to get that today or first thing tomorrow morning, and she could still proceed with surgery tomorrow.  She will also need chest x-ray and EKG. The testing was done and was negative.

